'''Lorell Hall''' was an assembly hall located in the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Ta'a Chume'Dan]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Hapes/Legends|Hapes]], the [[Capital/Legends|capital]] of the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]]. It stood with the royal palace on the bluffs overlooking the city, with vast [[Window/Legends|windows]] that allowed a dramatic view of the Hapan sky.

{{Struct-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
It is not entirely clear whether the Lorel Hall is part of the palace, or a separate structure. Adding to the confusion, sources disagree as to whether the palace overlooking Ta'a Chume'Dan is the real [[Fountain Palace]] or the royal spaceship ''[[Star Home]]'' on its surface landing-platform.

